TECHNICAL DETAILS
=================

Path Resolution Explanation:
-----------------------------
Playbooks location: ansible/roles/common/playbooks/
Task files location: ansible/roles/common/zFiles/
System tasks location: ansible/roles/common/tasks/

From playbooks/ directory:
- ../ = ansible/roles/common/
- ../zFiles/ = ansible/roles/common/zFiles/
- ../tasks/ = ansible/roles/common/tasks/

The broken paths used ../../../../ which would go:
../../../../ from playbooks/ = ansible/ (4 levels up)
Then tried to find compose/ and sysSettings/ which don't exist

Correct relative paths:
- ../zFiles/app.yml (1 level up, then into zFiles)
- ../tasks/system.yml (1 level up, then into tasks)

JavaScript Initialization Flow:
--------------------------------
1. Browser loads ansible_dashboard.html
2. HTML parser builds DOM tree
3. Script tag executes immediately (defines variables and functions)
4. DOMContentLoaded event fires when DOM is ready
5. Event listener executes:
   a. Load progress from localStorage
   b. Call initializeCharts() → creates 4 Chart.js charts
   c. Call recalculateAll() → calls populateTable() and renderPhaseTimeline()
   d. Setup filter button event listeners
   e. Setup search box event listener
6. User sees fully rendered dashboard with charts, tables, and interactive elements

