LESSONS LEARNED
===============

1. Always read files before editing - Edit tool requires Read first
2. Relative paths in Ansible must be from playbook's current directory
3. HTML/JavaScript requires explicit initialization code - definitions alone aren't enough
4. DOMContentLoaded prevents "element not found" errors with dynamic content
5. Syntax validation is crucial - ansible-playbook --syntax-check catches issues early
6. Documentation must be updated immediately after fixes to maintain accuracy

